ICS 1C Documentation Directory Dump

Below, one can find a listing of the contents of the documentation directory for ICS 1C.
Many of the documents here are linked to from elsewhere.
But like cobbler's children who have no shoes,
the document directory itself has no documentation beyond this feeble effort.

Everything comes to one who waits, except documentation.

This information brought to you by www.ics.uci.edu
Current as of 23 January 1995
Please send comments to ics1c@ics.uci.edu, including the URL to which your comments apply.
